P> </O:P></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P \r\nstyle=\"MARGIN-LEFT: 0.35in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.1in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; mso-list: l14 level1 lfo18; tab-stops: list .35in\"><FONT \r\nsize=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">·<SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; FONT-VARIANT: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\n</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">consistently alleviated \r\nthe plight of the poor in terms of education, health and employment \r\nprograms:<O:P> </O:P></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P \r\nstyle=\"MARGIN-LEFT: 0.85in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; mso-list: l14 level2 lfo18; tab-stops: list .85in\"><FONT \r\nsize=2><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">-<SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; FONT-VARIANT: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\n</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">Scholarship programs for \r\ncollege and high school students<O:P> </O:P></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P \r\nstyle=\"MARGIN-LEFT: 0.85in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; mso-list: l14 level2 lfo18; tab-stops: list .85in\"><FONT \r\nsize=2><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">-<SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; FONT-VARIANT: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\n</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">Libreng Palibing Program \r\nsince 1988<O:P> </O:P></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P \r\nstyle=\"MARGIN-LEFT: 0.85in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; mso-list: l14 level2 lfo18; tab-stops: list .85in\"><FONT \r\nsize=2><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">-<SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; FONT-VARIANT: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\n</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">Kalinga sa Kapwa \r\nMedical-Dental Assistance<O:P> </O:P></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P \r\nstyle=\"MARGIN-LEFT: 0.85in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; mso-list: l14 level2 lfo18; tab-stops: list .85in\"><FONT \r\nsize=2><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">-<SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; FONT-VARIANT: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\n</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">Justice on Wheels free \r\nlegal assistance program<O:P> </O:P></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P \r\nstyle=\"MARGIN-LEFT: 0.85in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; mso-list: l14 level2 lfo18; tab-stops: list .85in\"><FONT \r\nsize=2><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">-<SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; FONT-VARIANT: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\n</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">Grants and financial \r\nassistance to cooperatives, senior citizens &amp; people with \r\ndisability.&nbsp;<O:P> </O:P></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P \r\nstyle=\"MARGIN-LEFT: 0in; TEXT-INDENT: 0in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; mso-list: l19 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 9.0pt\"><FONT \r\nsize=2><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"COLOR: green; FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-style: italic\">ü<SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; FONT-VARIANT: normal\">&nbsp; \r\n</SPAN></SPAN><B><I><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"COLOR: green; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">DEFENDER OF OFW’s<O:P> \r\n</O:P></SPAN></I></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P \r\nstyle=\"MARGIN-LEFT: 0.35in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.1in; mso-list: l8 level1 lfo19; tab-stops: list .35in\"><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-FAMILY: Symbol\"><FONT size=2>·<SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; FONT-VARIANT: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\n</SPAN></FONT></SPAN><FONT size=2>author of RA 8042, the Migrant Workers Act \r\nwhich provides more support and protection to OFWs. Chairman of the first ever \r\ncongressional Committee on OFWs</FONT></P>\r\n<P \r\nstyle=\"MARGIN-LEFT: 0.35in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.1in; mso-list: l8 level1 lfo19; tab-stops: list .35in\"><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-FAMILY: Symbol\"><FONT size=2>·<SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; FONT-VARIANT: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\n</SPAN></FONT></SPAN><FONT size=2>instrumental in the implementation of a \r\nfinancial credit scheme to OFWs which is interest free, collateral free and \r\npractically pay-when-able system<B><I><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"COLOR: green; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">&nbsp;<O:P> \r\n</O:P></SPAN></I></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P \r\nstyle=\"MARGIN-LEFT: 0in; TEXT-INDENT: 0in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; mso-list: l19 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 9.0pt\"><FONT \r\nsize=2><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-bidi-font-style: italic\">ü<SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; FONT-VARIANT: normal\">&nbsp; \r\n</SPAN></SPAN><B><I><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"COLOR: green; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">CHAMPION OF THE \r\nPEOPLE</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\"><O:P> \r\n</O:P></SPAN></I></B></FONT></P>\r\n<P \r\nstyle=\"MARGIN-LEFT: 0.35in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.1in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo20; tab-stops: list .35in\"><FONT \r\nsize=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">·<SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; FONT-VARIANT: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\n</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">strong advocate of civil \r\nsociety and empowerment of NGOs and Pos<O:P> </O:P></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P \r\nstyle=\"MARGIN-LEFT: 0.35in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.1in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo20; tab-stops: list .35in\"><FONT \r\nsize=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">·<SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; FONT-VARIANT: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\n</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">1<SUP>st</SUP> Vice Pres. \r\nof the World Scout Parliamentary Union – the highest Filipino solon elected to \r\nthe post.<O:P> </O:P></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P \r\nstyle=\"MARGIN-LEFT: 0.35in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.1in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo20; tab-stops: list .35in\"><FONT \r\nsize=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">·<SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; FONT-VARIANT: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\n</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">Governor, Philippine \r\nNational Red Cross, Chairman, QC Red Cross, Chairman, QC Council Boy Scouts of \r\nthe Philippines, Knights of Rizal, QC-YMCA and Rotary Club of Tandang Sora, \r\nQC<O:P> </O:P></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P \r\nstyle=\"MARGIN-LEFT: 0.35in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.1in; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo20; tab-stops: list .35in\"><FONT \r\nsize=2><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">·<SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-WEIGHT: normal; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman; FONT-VARIANT: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\n</SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt\">known advocate for senior \r\ncitizens, disabled, victims of crime and injustice, youth and street \r\nchildren<O:P> </O:P></SPAN></FONT></P>','[Source: <A HREF=\"http://www.liban.faithweb.com/message.htm\">http://www.liban.faithweb.com/message.htm</A>]<BR><BR>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">30 \r\nMarch 2001</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">Dear \r\nFellow Citizens of Quezon City,&nbsp;<O:P> </O:P></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">I \r\nam humbled and overwhelmed by the prayers and encouragement I have received from \r\nnon-governmental organizations, professional groups and the business community, \r\nurging me to run for Mayor of Quezon City in the coming May 2001 elections. I \r\nhave accepted the challenge because, like you, I dream of a clean, peaceful, \r\nprosperous, illegal drug-free and pollution protected environment for my family \r\nin Quezon City. I believe that Quezon City has a destiny to fulfill, founded as \r\nit is on the noble ideals of the great Manuel Luis Quezon. Hence, we must waste \r\nno time in reclaiming long-lost glory as the former capital of the country and \r\nnow, as a premier, special first-class city, with limitless potentials for \r\ngrowth and development.</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">To \r\nall my fellow Quezon City residents, as one who has proudly lived in the the \r\ncity for the past 52 years, I humbly offer an unblemished 12-year track record \r\nin leadership and governance. My platform of government, geared at enabling \r\nQuezon City to meet the demands of the 21st century, is anchored on the \r\n</SPAN><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT \r\ncolor=#0000ff><B>10 E\'s of City Development:</B></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT \r\ncolor=#0000ff>ENVIRONMENT:</FONT></SPAN></B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> \r\nTo ensure effective garbage collection in all neighborhoods, each barangay will \r\ncollect, compost and recycle its own garbage with funds from City Hall to enable \r\nthem to buy its own mini-truck and mini-compactor. The extent of City Hall’s \r\nfinancial assistance to the barangays will vary depending on certain criteria \r\nparticularly relative cleanliness of the barangay. In addition, anti-littering, \r\nanti-public urinating and anti-pollution ordinances will be passed by the City \r\nCouncil.</SPAN><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">&nbsp;<O:P> \r\n</O:P></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT \r\ncolor=#0000ff>ERADICATION GRAFT AND CORRUPTION:</FONT></SPAN></B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> \r\nCity Hall will request the Ombudsman deploy a resident-ombudsman in City Hall to \r\nreceive and investigate any complaint of corruption against any official. \r\nBureaucratic red tape will be eliminated through the establishment of a one-stop \r\nprocessing center, which will process applications and release the same within \r\n24 hours.<SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </SPAN>All public projects will \r\nbe awarded through public biddings, and all public transactions will pass \r\nthrough pre-audit procedures.&nbsp;<O:P> </O:P></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT \r\ncolor=#0000ff>ENFORCEMENT OF LAWS:</FONT></SPAN><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> \r\n</SPAN></B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">Regaining \r\nthe trust and faith of the people in the strict enforcement of laws and city \r\nordinances shall be a top priority program. We shall always enlist people’s \r\nparticipation in the over-all campaign against drugs, alcoholism, fraternity \r\nviolence and other vices. Police, barangay and community action must be enhanced \r\nat all times.</SPAN><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">&nbsp;<O:P> \r\n</O:P></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT \r\ncolor=#0000ff>EMPLOYMENT:</FONT></SPAN></B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> \r\nFollowing the mandate of an ordinance I authored as a city councilor, city \r\nresidents shall be given top priority in all employment opportunities, both in \r\nprivate and in the city government. City Hall will conduct regular skills \r\ntraining and cross-training to the jobless sector of the community. To attract \r\nbusinessmen to Quezon City, and thus generate jobs, City Hall will provide them \r\nwith the necessary infrastructure and telecommunications facilities as well as \r\nred tape-free environment.</SPAN><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">&nbsp;<O:P> \r\n</O:P></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT \r\ncolor=#0000ff>EDUCATION:</FONT></SPAN></B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> \r\nRealizing that QC is the only city in Metro Manila without a city college, we \r\nshall establish the Quezon City Polytechnic College to enable deserving but poor \r\npublic high school graduates to pursue college education. We shall give emphasis \r\nto science and technology. Moreover, a huge, modern and complete public library \r\nwill be built, where citizens can do research through computers and over the \r\ninternet for free.</SPAN><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">&nbsp;<O:P> \r\n</O:P></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT \r\ncolor=#0000ff>EXTENSION OF LIFE EXPECTANCY:</FONT></SPAN></B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> \r\nThe Quezon City General Hospital will be rehabilitated, expanded and modernized. \r\nHealth Centers will be made available to the poor in each barangay with a \r\nprovision for a full-time doctor with the capability to do minor surgery. City \r\nHall will tie up with private civic organizations like Rotary, Lions and Kiwanis \r\nfor regular and rotating medical missions in all the barangays. Rolling \r\ndrugstores selling affordable medicine, sponsored either by City Hall or a \r\npharmaceutical company, will rove the barangays at pre-announced \r\nschedules.</SPAN><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">&nbsp;<O:P> \r\n</O:P></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT \r\ncolor=#0000ff>EXCELLENCE IN SPORTS:</FONT></SPAN></B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> \r\nWe shall pursue a year round sports development program. We shall work for the \r\nestablishment of a sports center in every congressional district to insure the \r\nprovision of facilities and the undertaking of events. We shall regard sports as \r\nan effective counteractive program against drug addiction, youth alcoholism and \r\nthe prevalence of teenage marriages.</SPAN><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">&nbsp;<O:P> \r\n</O:P></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT \r\ncolor=#0000ff>EMPOWERMENT OF THE BARANGAYS:</FONT></SPAN></B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> \r\nThe barangay will be given opportunities to grow and develop itself in terms of \r\nfiscal management to enable good governance. We shall adapt a policy to empower \r\nbarangays to pre-qualify bids and award contracts. Shares in the Internal \r\nRevenue Allotment (IRA) and the Real Property Tax (RPT) must be automatically \r\nremitted to the bank account of the barangay council to enable it to plan and \r\neffectively budget its resources.</SPAN><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">&nbsp;<O:P> \r\n</O:P></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT \r\ncolor=#0000ff>EMPOWERMENT OF WOMEN:</FONT></SPAN><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> \r\n</SPAN></B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">With \r\nthe establishment of a Center for Women in Development, we shall conduct \r\ncontinuing education program, skills training, and entrepreneurial and \r\nlivelihood projects to enable our women to become active participants in all \r\nphases of development at the barangay and community level.</SPAN><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">&nbsp;<O:P> \r\n</O:P></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><FONT \r\ncolor=#0000ff>EXEMPLARY LEADERSHIP:</FONT></SPAN><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"> \r\n</SPAN></B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">The \r\nCity Mayor and all public officials of Quezon City must always seek to lead by \r\nexample. In consonance with their divine faith, public servants must practice a \r\nlife beyond moral reproach, an in so doing remain faithful to the people they \r\nhave sworn to serve. We shall promulgate a code of ethics for all city \r\nofficials.</SPAN><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">&nbsp;<O:P> \r\n</O:P></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">After \r\nall is said and done, I sincerely hope that the decision as to who will lead \r\nQuezon City in the New Millennium will not be based on the two trivial P\'s - \r\n<I>papogihan </I>or popularity but one the real P\'s </SPAN><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">- \r\n<O:P></O:P></SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">Public \r\nService based on an excellent track record and a <O:P></O:P></SPAN></B></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">Personal \r\nLife based on Christian living and a happy family.</SPAN></B><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">&nbsp;</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">God \r\nbless you always.</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">Ang \r\ninyong lingkod bayan,</SPAN></P>\r\n<P class=MsoBodyText style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><SPAN \r\nstyle=\"FONT-SIZE: 8pt; COLOR: windowtext; FONT-STYLE: normal; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><B>DANTE \r\nVENTURA LIBAN<O:P> &nbsp;</B></SPAN></P>','','[Source: <A HREF=\"http://www.liban.faithweb.com/family.htm\">http://www.liban.faithweb.com/family.htm</A>]<BR><BR>\r\n<P>\r\nHonorable Dante V. Liban is a man of values and a family man, an exemplary father to his children Jing-Jing, Cheekee, Luzee, Kring-Kring and Carlo. He is a doting and devoted husband to his wife of 26 years, the former Marvina de Leon Reina of La Paz, Iloilo and Talipapa, Novaliches, Quezon City.\r\n<P>\r\nJing-jing is currently a graduating law student at the University of the Philippines.  Cheekee after obtaining her Child Psychology degree in UP is pursuing her medical studies at the University of Massachusetts in Boston.  Kring-kring is an incoming freshman who will take up Communications Technology Management.  Luzee is a 3rd year high school student while perky Carlo is a 6th grader.\r\n<P>\r\nHis wife, fondly called Baby by many has matched Liban’s devotion to his family with equal intensity. She gave up her post as vice president for a multinational firm in Makati City just to be able to devote her time attending to the needs of her family and her husband’s constituents. Now, Congressman and Mrs. Liban are busy devoting their lives answering the needs of the people. The successful tandem of Dante and Baby Liban only proves the truth of the dictum that behind the success of every man is a woman. Liban is also an active Catholic lay leader in Church through his membership in the Couples for Christ. He is a firm believer in the saying: \"No amount of success can ever compensate for failure in the home.\"','','','liban@pacific.net.ph','','932-9990; 428-5015',0,20010521155209,'','','','',61233,0,'N');
