st District, Quezon City from 1992 to March 1998</B><BR> \r\nMinority Floor Leader - City Council, Quezon CIty form 1993 to 1995 <BR>\r\nMajority Floor Leader - City Council, Quezon City from 1995 to 1998 <BR>\r\nPracticing Lawyer - Since 1979 continuously up to present <BR>\r\nLaw Professor - College of Law, Adamson University since 1983 up to present <BR> \r\nHead - Samson Montesa Alcid Villacorta and Associates <BR>\r\nLegal Consultant - Office of the City Vice Mayor, Caloocan City <BR> \r\nFormer Law Associate - Subido Law Office <BR>\r\nFormer Legal Researcher - Mariano & Associates Law Office <BR> \r\nFormer Legal Consultant - City Council, Manila <BR>\r\nLecturer - Katarungang Pambarangay Law and Other Related Laws <BR>\r\nAuthor - Book on Katarungang Pambarangay Law <BR>','','','Balintawak, Quezon City','','','373-3849 / 373-3478',0,20010521153648,'','','Etet','',36324,1,'N');
